software.leonov.common.util.function

Interface CheckedBinaryOperator<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CheckedBiFunction<T,T,T>
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface CheckedBinaryOperator<T>
extends CheckedBiFunction<T,T,T>
    Mirror of the BinaryOperator interface whose apply(T, T) method can throw a checked exception.
